{"tid":1177721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"父母分居真係好撚麻煩","createTime":"2019-05-30T02:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T02:38:31.000Z","uid":233530,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5626529436f40ec48090866aea2feeee9f833eb9","tid":1177721,"uid":233530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"仆街老豆七年前爭咗街數幾廿萬走咗佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆老母冇正式離婚<br />\n結果搞到我而家周身屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細到大都因為唔齊文件拎唔到任何資助<br />\n書簿津貼又冇 車船津貼又冇<br />\n公屋個戶主又係老豆個名<br />\n而家逢親搞入息申報之類都麻煩到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最仆街係學資處<br />\n一係人 一係離婚證<br />\n屌你老母佢賭輸咗幾廿萬著草 你同我講離婚證<br />\n我點撚樣嘔畀你呀大佬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家屋企靠老母搵得嗰萬幾蚊過世<br />\n我已經預咗畢業出嚟要孭成廿萬學債<br />\n仲要成世人孭住頭家<br />\n究竟可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3117747fd07ce4d1b28f04ad6e2b51e770d29f1e","tid":1177721,"uid":131404,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:21:40.000Z","msg":"可以上網查下<br />\n分居兩年已經可以單方面申請離婚"},{"pid":"5435668e0bab4e903d1b9ba708a2757a3ffdc82f","tid":1177721,"uid":106296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3117747fd07ce4d1b28f04ad6e2b51e770d29f1e","tid":1177721,"uid":131404,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:21:40.000Z","msg":"可以上網查下<br />\n分居兩年已經可以單方面申請離婚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"我都想講"},{"pid":"2ce55a33e9ac12f89cd8e9636bd8d25052aa5b0a","tid":1177721,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:24:11.000Z","msg":"老公著草，老母咁辛苦養大你，真係要對佢好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a47fcbd266fe6e95ec784ac4b10c156ae419cef","tid":1177721,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ce55a33e9ac12f89cd8e9636bd8d25052aa5b0a","tid":1177721,"uid":16647